    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "text": "# Letter to shareholders\n\nFY2026 was a year of disciplined growth. Revenue grew **68% year over year** while operating costs grew 42%, moving the company to within one quarter of break-even.\n\nWe kept three promises made in last year’s letter: we shipped the self-serve tier, we brought gross margin above 70%, and we did it without doubling headcount.\n\n## Highlights\n\n- ARR crossed **$1.8M** in June 2026.\n- Net revenue retention reached **112%**.\n- The self-serve tier now accounts for **31%** of new logos."
    },
