      "type": "markdown",
      "text": "# Financial review\n\n## Revenue quality\n\nRecurring revenue represented 94% of total revenue, up from 88% in FY2025. Services revenue is deliberately flat: we productize instead of staffing.\n\n## Cost structure\n\nInfrastructure cost per active customer fell 23% after the March storage migration. Sales efficiency (magic number) ended the year at **0.9**."
