      "type": "markdown",
      "text": "# Outlook\n\n## FY2027 priorities\n\n1. Break even by Q2 FY2027 without slowing R&D.\n2. Land the first ten enterprise logos in regulated industries.\n3. Keep infrastructure cost growth below half of revenue growth.\n\n## Risks\n\nConcentration: the top ten customers are 38% of ARR. Mitigation is the self-serve motion, which spreads revenue across 1,400+ small accounts."
